subtitleNullable: Binary image classification on Flower images
descriptionNullable:
### Context

The dataset consists of flower images and will help you in creating a binary image classification model.


### Content

The images are divided into two classes: Daisy & Non-Daisy
For each class, there are ~400 images. All the images are not of high resolution but are about 320x240 pixels.


### Acknowledgements

All the images are scraped from Flickr, Google images, and Yandex images.
